message.body: Hey! My flight time changed and if all goes well land at 9:05... Sorry that it's early on a Saturday!
Does that still work?
Yeahhhh!
Oh I love you! Hey, where do you live now btw? St Paul or mpls?
I live in uptown now
I had a kidney stone last night.
Oh awesome! I miss that neighborhood
Oh god!! Are you ok??
Just so you know.....I might not be able to get crazy drank.....
Yeah I am fine now. Still need to pee it out but thankfully it has passed.
Oh that's totally fine - I'm taking easy these days too. My boyfriend, also named Scott, just passed a kidney stone a couple days ago too. Did you have to go to the hospital?
Yea I did. I have never had one before so I was just very concerned.
Oh I know how painful it is based on Scott... Are you feeling better now?
Yeah my groin still hurts a little but doing better.
Ugh well good. Hey, do you have a couch I could crash on tomorrow night? I'm sorry to spring that on you - my plan with trav fell through...
Of course!
You're very sweet
Is that photo on your phone cause ew... But omg that latest episode
Yes it is. For any moment's use.....but that latest episode. Scary and out of control
Got seats on both planes so im running on time :)
